  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">周末看到一个好玩的东西。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">3D领域的NanoBanana也来了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"500195506\" data-ratio=\"1.6081081081081081\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"592\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=5b92a2c7&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURqUwSPZLxXfTiaI97M9ldoF7Sw1tLGic3BhG3sLc5hibTn4mNkps5zP9ThCCHV8icHBSBWNKFvRcXibxBw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">中间有一句比较重要的功能，是我觉得非常有意思的：</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">可以通过提示进行局部编辑。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: normal;\">玩过NanoBanana的肯定很熟了。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">算了补全了一块有意思的拼图。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">放下他们的视频。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">用嘴来修改一切，真的变成了一个是未来必然的趋势。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">图片领域有Nano Banana、视频领域有可灵o1，现在3D领域，hyper3D带着他们的Rodin Gen-2也来了。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这现在应该是第一个也是唯一一个，能用嘴编辑3D模型的AI3D产品。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">而且是你能上传任意的三方模型上去，进行修改和编辑。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">还是蛮有意思的。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">真的，2019年我在学C4D学Blender，在那kuku的手拉box在那渲染模型的时候，真的没想过这么一天。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">原来动动嘴，就可以改模型了啊...</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">网址在此：</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://hyper3d.ai/\" target=\"_blank\">https://hyper3d.ai/</a></span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">进来以后，有两个卡片，一个是图生3D模型。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5262738853503185\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1256\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500195512\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=9a5a9d13&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURqUwSPZLxXfTiaI97M9ldoF7icqAwtgCZLaXHEs2icMqM5LmRZl2DsiajdvZtSvJrGHJbe8P1CBvFRWlA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-bottom: 24px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">另一个就是直接上传任意一个obj、fbx之类的3D模型，就可以直接进行编辑。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6143497757847534\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"669\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500195513\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=24c72a44&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURqUwSPZLxXfTiaI97M9ldoF7yCYr2dB4qyBf06a6SCQibInwwryTphwI90TV6lUWOicYLQRldFpx2xkA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-bottom: 24px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">而这个功能，才是我觉得，最牛逼的。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-bottom: 24px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">你完全可以对任意的三方模型，进行二创。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-bottom: 24px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">比如我随手可以去</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">sketchfab上下载一个很爆的模型扔到了Blender里，它长这样。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5601851851851852\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500195550\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=adf9b1a2&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURqUwSPZLxXfTiaI97M9ldoF7qzgDmt1DDrZqZdYwuTnPib0TNSxLojiaUsWTyLabZoDrFbialcxJfPfqA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">过去，想改这种级别的模型，真的非常的麻烦，不管你是自己3D打印玩，还是想做个独立游戏扔进去当个BOSS，还是做个片子去K动画，都是一个非常复杂的事情。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">比如我想把它的斧头改成大剑，现在，你只需要扔到</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">hyper3d的Rodin里，然后，用嘴改就行。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">真的，一句话，就是这个效果，极其牛逼。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这就是用嘴改模型的魅力啊。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">考虑到大多数普通玩家，可能还没有玩过3D，所以，我直接用从头到尾的图生3D模型的流程，来给大家看看，能怎么玩。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">给大家先看个例子。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-bottom: 24px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">比如说我这里有个高达图，是之前用NanoBanana生成的，我还蛮喜欢的。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"500195514\" data-ratio=\"1.2649739583333333\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1536\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=0d576ae8&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURqUwSPZLxXfTiaI97M9ldoF7T4CYvlp8Ce5mjOLNETdWicicTicM7NA7GqkCYTRRttciab3QgYEOnrNkuQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-bottom: 24px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我们直接给它上传上去。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-bottom: 24px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">然后，大概几十秒之后，一个模型就出来了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6694444444444444\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500195515\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=8a2602df&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURqUwSPZLxXfTiaI97M9ldoF7fdoNQvGYmoPEV4EK7fERicIaERlViba8CWRD4jU8h5eNhkaGdEJNgoPA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-bottom: 24px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这个模型其实还有很多问题，比如翅膀我才发现只有一边，缺了一半。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">翅膀跟主体之间的关联，也是没有的，是之间悬空的。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.8944281524926686\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"682\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500195516\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c0012e64&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURqUwSPZLxXfTiaI97M9ldoF7fFuribibSL1H22XKsY5Vl1mZosdzRDtRc8uI7x2BJU8w7iaRRfsVicpRXw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">但是没关系，我们可以修改。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">手悬浮到那个重做上，然后就会看到上面冒出来一个修改的按钮。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6638888888888889\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500195518\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=9d4bc57b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURqUwSPZLxXfTiaI97M9ldoF7aEGOVuYg7QAwrr0NficLSqGA7EaMm6bf36ufwOZBkrmQuWWR15Jb40A%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">虽然我也不知道他们为啥不把修改放出来而是要藏在那。。。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">选择修改以后，你就能看到出来了一个还非常有科技感的框框。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6694560669456067\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"478\" style=\"width: 100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"478\" data-backh=\"320\" data-imgfileid=\"500195519\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=a66cb6fd&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_gif%2FOjgKEXmLURqUwSPZLxXfTiaI97M9ldoF7YHjuVjGeiaLnmU0X3acfxDCwzdvtHchvupzs5DuSNDiahhs9uNObn8sA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这个交互也非常的有意思。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">就是你把模型的区域放在框内，当你看到模型的那部分变成了水波纹那种形状的时候，就说明，那块被选中了。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">在下面的选项里，我们选择局部修改。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">可以看到有三个选项。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.46774